{"tid":2302814,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)奪寶奇兵1-3","createTime":"2020-11-27T11:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T18:03:19.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"04fa3b38c9f3518cd3879859f55e1243576bd309","tid":2302814,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T11:52:27.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpDv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=c104ade0\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpDv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=573be079\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpDv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=3a00fbe4\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/4b/Raiders.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F4b%2FRaiders.jpg&h=c4e52631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.1936年，寶物獵人及考古學家印第安納&middot;瓊斯勇闖秘魯叢林，在充滿危險機關的古廟中尋找黃金神像。逃出古廟後，他卻遇見競爭對手：另一個考古學家瑞尼貝拉克以及他率領的土人，被迫交出他找到的金像。突破重圍後，印第安納&middot;瓊斯登上一艘早就安排好的水上飛機逃離了叢林。<br />\n短暫停留美國後，他回到校園教授考古學。兩個陸軍情報人員到他的學校告訴他，德國納粹黨正在追求未知的神秘武力，並在追捕他的老師艾伯納瑞文伍德。瑞文伍德擁有稱為「拉雅之桿」頂端的元件<br />\n<br />\n2.1935年，考古學教授印第安納&middot;瓊斯帶著夜總會歌女威莉和12歲的孤兒小滑溜在中國上海一起逃命冒險，逃脫後意外到了一個破落的印度小村莊，這個小村落的所有幼童和村裡的3塊珍貴聖石都失蹤了。印第安納&middot;瓊斯承諾協助村長尋回失蹤的3塊珍貴聖石和兒童外，來到了盤踞邪惡勢力控制的王室宮殿，找出3塊具有神秘法力的寶石。印第安納&middot;瓊斯他們再度展開驚險的鬥智鬥力和奪寶追逐戰<br />\n<br />\n3.考古學教授印第安納&middot;瓊斯的父親亨利&middot;瓊斯教授，因為研究並尋找傳說中的耶穌聖杯而失蹤。由於德國納粹黨也要奪取有神奇力量的聖杯，印第安納&middot;瓊斯和父親必須在奧地利及德國納粹黨軍隊追殺下冒險死裡逃生。<br />\n<br />\n8 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完左可能播驚天奪寶<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpDv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=24d5e0ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpDv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=92ec9a51\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f92dfd177edd23f9292a903cae94e6bc859a21","tid":2302814,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T11:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a1688f5759a40dd2776b77ca2f5f52d2a980b7","tid":2302814,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT